{"tid":1469570,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"就呢幾日喺連登發生嘅事，想同手足講幾句","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:30:00.000Z","uid":164606,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e49206b1b32b7610c836cb7e87cf375d4b0a85d9","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發生左好多事，喺連登都見到個勢有啲分裂，因此想講幾句<br />\n總路線嚟講，想大家睇翻呢個post:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家係抗爭關鍵時期!大家真係要傾!</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426270/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426270/page/1</a><br />\n但想大家留意翻兩樣野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 勿厚此薄彼</span></span><br />\n唔知點解各手足係連登都鍾意屌咗同路人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時前線做咗啲咩觀感唔好嘅野就大大力屌/同帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係前線都比你地屌到心灰啦 將心比己啦</span></span><br />\n對家(aka狗畜同藍絲)犯錯都只係講幾句就算<br />\n試吓多啲提醒，少啲屌屌屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔完美，可接受，但亦都要改善</span></span><br />\n同埋用吓腦諗邊啲係帶風向post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 試吓習慣用不推文功能</span></span><br />\n呢個功能簡直係連仔比我地嘅恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多時有好多假膠/分化post留多啲言就上咗熱門 之後睇個啲人就信咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />'<br />\n用呢個功能就可以防止呢樣野發生 又可以屌到班臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />\\<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應承我，今日開始習慣用呢個功能好冇?</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8a736a31110bd4dfb3ce6071b51271aac5a5dc9","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"818見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693c9ba699cebff984f86f551e73c6919a11c24f","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"e027ea11c62efaa03dd317af3692b72ecf97ed3c","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"5294c1a0d23e27f160aa484752736d4c2b8a9013","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3ba6d3691b9cada4eaa19f867f7850373e6ae2","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957cf6a9d65b6b6c509a42e1b7dbf1155fa52752","tid":1469570,"uid":164606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\